    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "According to https://github.com/mono/mono/blob/master/mcs/class/corlib/System/Environment.cs#L619 we want to use`SpecialFolder.ApplicationData` and `SpecialFolder.LocalApplicationData` (if we want split config/data) on Linux.\n\nWe should also change to `SpecialFolder.CommonApplicationData` on Windows â€“ this maps to `C:/ProgramData` on recent versions, and is shared for all users.  It maps to `/usr/share` on Linux, so it isn't usable there.\n"
  },
